<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Тригонометрични функции – 9. клас</title>

  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255,255,255,0.80) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 34%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #eef2ff 0%, #f8fafc 50%, #eff6ff 100%);
      color: #1e293b;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 56px 20px 42px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255,255,255,0.24), transparent 36%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #4338ca);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.22);
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    header p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 650;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1050px;
      margin: 38px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .intro {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 28px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(67, 56, 202, 0.10);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .intro h2 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: #2563eb;
      font-size: 1.65rem;
    }

    .intro p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .lesson-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(270px, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .lesson-card {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #1e293b;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.90);
      border: 1px solid rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.92);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.12);
      transition: transform 0.22s ease, box-shadow 0.22s ease, border-color 0.22s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 250px;
    }

    .lesson-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(59,130,246,0.18), transparent 38%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .lesson-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.16);
      border-color: #60a5fa;
    }

    .icon {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: 58px;
      height: 58px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe, #c7d2fe);
      color: #2563eb;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 18px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.14);
    }

    .icon svg {
      width: 31px;
      height: 31px;
      stroke: currentColor;
      fill: none;
      stroke-width: 2;
      stroke-linecap: round;
      stroke-linejoin: round;
    }

    .lesson-card h3 {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      color: #1d4ed8;
      font-size: 1.28rem;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .lesson-card p {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.52;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .badge {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 13px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #dbeafe;
      color: #1e40af;
      font-weight: 850;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .back-link {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }

    .back-link a {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: white;
      color: #2563eb;
      padding: 12px 22px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(120, 110, 150, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .back-link a:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(120, 110, 150, 0.16);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 28px 20px 40px;
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      header {
        padding: 46px 18px 36px;
      }

      .container {
        padding: 0 16px;
      }

      .intro {
        padding: 22px 18px;
      }

      .lesson-card {
        border-radius: 22px;
        padding: 22px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Тригонометрични функции</h1>
    <p>9. клас</p>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <section class="intro">
      <h2>Уроци и интерактивни ресурси</h2>
      <p>Избери ресурс, за да отвориш интерактивния урок.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="lesson-grid">

      <a class="lesson-card" href="https://valyavitkovska.github.io/trigonometrichni-funkcii-na-ostar-agal/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M4 18h16"></path>
            <path d="M4 18l8-12 8 12"></path>
            <path d="M8 18v-4h4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Тригонометрични функции на остър ъгъл</h3>
        <p>Интерактивен урок със симулация, теория, тест и практически задачи за синус, косинус, тангенс и котангенс.</p>
        <span class="badge">Отвори урока</span>
      </a>

    </section>

    <div class="back-link">
      <a href="../">← Обратно към 9. клас</a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    Математика с Валя Витковска
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
